<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />아 참!<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> 지금은 지구의 날 기간이니까<delay20 />
